	<ThingDef ParentName="GunPartBase">
		<defName>Module_Vampir</defName>
		<label>ZG 1229 "Vampir" x1.5 Scope</label>
		<description>The Zielger√§t 1229, also known by its code name "Vampir", was an active infrared device developed for the Wehrmacht for the Sturmgewehr 44 assault rifle during World War II, intended primarily for night use.</description>
		<statBases>
